title: Appointments to the Hospital Authority announced
content_text: The Government announced today (Friday) the appointment of two members and the re-appointment of 11 members to the Hospital Authority (HA). Mr Anthony Wu Ting-yuk and Dr Thomas Wong Kwok-shing are appointed to be members of HA for two years with effect from 1 December 1999. Mr Anthony Wu Ting-yuk, an experienced accountant, has been active in public services. He is now a member of the Hospital

accountant, has been active in public services. He is now a member of the Hospital Governing Committee of the Pamela Youde Nethersole Eastern Hospital. Dr Thomas Wong Kwok-shing is the Associate Head of the Department of Nursing and Health Sciences of the Hong Kong Polytechnic University. He is also a member of the Hong Kong Nursing Council.
